<F P=100> PRC MEDIA ON TAIWAN AFFAIRS </F>
<H3> <TI>   China Southern Airlines Passenger Plane Hijacked </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    China Southern Airlines Passenger Plane Hijacked </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Diversion to Taiwan </H4>

<F P=102> OW0606140494 Beijing XINHUA in English 1354 GMT 6 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW0606140494 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, June 6 (XINHUA) -- A Chinese domestic 
passenger plane was highjacked to Taiwan today. 
  A spokesman for the Civil Aviation Administration of China 
(CAAC) said that China Southern Airlines' B-737/2542 passenger 
plane was serving the CZ3572 flight from Fuzhou to Guangzhou. 
It took off at 18:58 from Fuzhou Airport, and was highjacked on 
its flight. At 19:57 it landed safely at Taoyuan Airport, 
Taibei [Taipei]. 
  The spokesman said that relevant departments of the two 
sides 
of the Taiwan Straits are in contact on the incident. 

</TEXT>

