sourceline reads: ...[By reporter Zhang Yijun (1728 4135 0193)] 
-- China announced here... (supplying reporter's name) 
  Paragraph five, sentence one reads: ...of imported goods 
effective today [zi ji ri qi 5261 0613 2480 6386]. [new graf] 
  The announcement was... (providing effective date) 
  Column two, first full paragraph, only sentence, reads: ...a 
protocol package on China's "reentry into GATT" will be 
discussed... (supplying additional words) 

