  [Text] Beijing, June 7 (XINHUA) -- State Councillor Li 
Tieying met here today with Dan Ikuma, deputy director of the 
Japan-China Culture Exchanges Association, and his party. 
  During the meeting in the Great Hall of the People, they 
exchanged views on enhancing understanding and cooperation 
