<F P=100> NATIONAL AFFAIRS </F>
<F P=101> Political &amp; Social </F>
<H3> <TI>   CPC Committee Holds Ideological, Political Conference </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    CPC Committee Holds Ideological, Political Conference </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW0706143494 Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service in Chinese 0711 
GMT 7 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> OW0706143494 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA Domestic Service </F>
<F P=105>  Chinese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [By RENMIN RIBAO reporter Xu Rujun (1776 1172 0193) and </F>
XINHUA reporter Hu Qinghai (5170 3237 3189)] 
  [Text] Beijing, 7 Jun (XINHUA) -- The Work Committee for 
CPC Central Committee Organs held a work conference on 
ideological and political work in Beijing today. Work Committee 
Secretary Zeng Qinghong pointed out at the meeting: Ideological 
and political work plays an important role in the party's entire 
cause. It is a crucial link that helps transform the party's 
line, principles, and policy into the masses' action of 
consciousness, an important approach that helps unite the masses 
of people and arouse their initiative, and a vital force and 
important guarantee for the smooth progress of revolution and 
construction. 
  Zeng Qinghong said: Paying high regard to ideological and 
political work and giving full play to the role of ideological 
and political work is our party's fine tradition and politically 
strong points. As the administrative body of the CPC Central 
Committee, CPC Central Committee organs shoulder important 
responsibilities for formulating and carrying out the party's 
line, principles, and policy and play an important pivotal role 
in the party's cause. The position and role of the CPC Central 
Committee organs set higher and stricter demands on the masses 
of cadres and personnel in terms of politics, work style, and 
administration. 
  Zeng Qinghong demanded that the ideological and political 
work of the CPC Central Committee organs must be guided by 
Comrade Deng Xiaoping's theory of building socialism with 
Chinese characteristics and the party's basic line and closely 
centered around the party's central tasks. The CPC Central 
Committee organs must make efforts in ideological and political 
work to meet the needs of the developing circumstances and 
closely integrate it with administrative affairs of various 
departments and units. They must conscientiously strengthen 
ideological education; improve overall quality of their cadres 
and personnel; and cultivate a team of cadres and personnel who 
are promising, moral, cultured, and self-disciplined. They must 
fully arouse the enthusiasm, initiative, and creativeness of 
cadres and personnel; ensure the completion of various tasks in 
their departments and units; and serve the deepening of reform, 
promoting of development, and maintaining of stability. 
  Zeng Qinghong said emphatically: To arm the entire party 
with Comrade Deng Xiaoping's theory of building socialism with 
Chinese characteristics is a major task of party building in the 
new period and a major task of the ideological and political 
work in the new situation. The fundamental goal of the CPC 
Central Committee organs' ideological and political work is to 
unite the ideology of the masses of cadres and personnel with 
Comrade Deng Xiaoping's theory of building socialism with 
Chinese characteristics and the party's basic line. Party 
organizations at all levels in CPC Central Committee organs must 
conscientiously and carefully study the theory in an in-depth 
manner. He added: Comrade Deng Xiaoping made a series of 
important expositions on the ideological and political work in 
the new period. These expositions have substantial content, 
deep intention, and distinct features of the times. These 
expositions are an important part of his theory of building 
socialism with Chinese characteristics. The masses of party 
members and cadres, especially those who are involved in 
ideological and political work, must conscientiously study these 
expositions, grasp their essence, and use these expositions as a 
guide to their work. 
  Gu Yunfei, deputy secretary of the Work Committee for CPC 
Central Committee Organs, presided over the meeting. 

</TEXT>

