  [Text] Beijing, June 9 (CNS)--China's Vice Premier and 
Foreign Minister Mr Qian Qichen said to South Korean Foreign 
Minister Han Sung-chu today that China held the two basic 
targets should be set for settlement of the issue of the nuclear 
fuel in North Korea. They were to promote denuclearization in 
the Korean Peninsula and to safeguard peace and stability in the 
