and should not shut the door of negotiations. China appealed to 
the sides concerned to continue making efforts to restart talks 
so as to leave room and possibility for settlement of the issue. 
  Mr Qian also said to impose sanctions would not help solve 
the problem. On the contrary, it might lead to consequences 
which no one wished to see. 

