  [Text] PRC President Jiang Zemin said in Beijing on 7 June 
that strengthening and developing PRC-DPRK friendship is the 
unwavering policy of the CPC and the PRC Government, as well as 
the desire of the whole party and all the people. 
  During a meeting with a DPRK military delegation led by Vice 
Marshal Choe Kwang, chief of general staff of the Korea People's 
Army, President Jiang Zemin said that the PRC and the DPRK are 
