  [Text] At the invitation of Jilin Province, the 
eight-member friendly delegation from Chagang Province of the 
DPRK, led by Kim Chong-ho, chairman of the Chagang Provincial 
Administrative and Economic Committee of the DPRK, arrived in 
Changchun by train on 26 May to make an official friendly visit 
to our province. 
  Governor Gao Yan cordially met with all delegation members 
at 
